text: Hi <@U07512EJXP1>! Did you ever find a way to resolve this issue? I am having the same issue again. I contacted HubSpot support but they have been unresponsive.

Same problem here - but I don't think this is just a HubSpot thing.  I have also seen this on Google Search Console on redirects.  Search Console and HubSpots tools both hate redirects.  If you are on Wordpress....which we are, there are lots of redirects when you think about archives, etc.
